---
import SiteLayout from "../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Support | NextMetro"
  description="Get help with NextMetro, the iPhone and Apple Watch app for knowing when to leave for the next train."
>
  <section class="section tight content-page">
    <p class="eyebrow">Support</p>
    <h1>Help for your next ride.</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Need help with setup, predictions, notifications, or station choices?
      We can help get NextMetro back on track.
    </p>

    <div class="contact-panel panel">
      <h2>Email Support</h2>
      <p>
        Send a note to <a href="mailto:support@nextmetro.app">support@nextmetro.app</a>
        with your device model, app version, station, route, and what you expected
        to see.
      </p>
      <a class="button primary" href="mailto:support@nextmetro.app">Contact Support</a>
    </div>

    <div class="content-block">
      <h2>Common Questions</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          If setup is blocked, add a WMATA API key on iPhone and sync settings to
          Apple Watch.
        </li>
        <li>
          If train times look stale, check your network connection and reopen the
          app to refresh predictions.
        </li>
        <li>
          If alerts are missing, confirm notifications are enabled for NextMetro
          in your device settings.
        </li>
        <li>
          If a station or line is unavailable, include the station name and route
          in your support email.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
